com.nexmo.sdk.core.verify

Enum UserStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UserStatus>
      • com.nexmo.sdk.core.verify.UserStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UserStatus>

    public enum UserStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<UserStatus>
    User status codes.
    • Each verify flow starts from a USER_NEW status.
    • After call is successful, the user status will be changed to USER_PENDING. From this moment on, the user is expected to receive a PIN code.
    • User can get into USER_FAILED status if incorrect pin was entered 3 times.
    • User can get into USER_EXPIRED status if the correct PIN was not entered in due time.
